  "text": [
    "First hold the needle",
    "like a lover\u2019s hand",
    "Lower it slowly",
    "let it tongue",
    "the record\u2019s ear",
    "Then cultivate",
    "the sweet beats",
    "blooming in the valley",
    "of the groove",
    "Laugh at folks",
    "that make requests",
    "What chef would let",
    "the diners determine",
    "Which entrees",
    "make up the menu?",
    "Young boys",
    "think it\u2019s about",
    "flashy flicks",
    "of the wrist",
    "But it\u2019s about filling the floor",
    "with the manic",
    "language of dance",
    "About knowing the beat",
    "of every record",
    "like a mama knows",
    "her child\u2019s cries",
    "Nobody cares",
    "how fast you scratch",
    "Cuz it ain\u2019t about",
    "soothing any itch",
    "It\u2019s about how many hairstyles",
    "At the end of the night."
  ],
  "title": "Turning the Tables",
  "year": ""
}